org.sxb.data.redis.support.collections

インタフェース RedisZSet<E>

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    BoundKeyOperations<java.lang.String>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, RedisCollection<E>, RedisStore, java.util.Set<E>
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DefaultRedisZSet

    public interface RedisZSet<E>
extends RedisCollection<E>, java.util.Set<E>
    Redis ZSet (or sorted set (by weight)). Acts as a SortedSet based on the given priorities or weights associated with each item.

    Since using a Comparator does not apply, a ZSet implements the SortedSet methods where applicable.

    作成者:
    Costin Leau
